  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Delp</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Delp</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully_guards\" title=\"House Tully guards\">guard</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Delp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Delp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Delp is on duty at the River Gate when <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a>'s plot to break Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> free is carried out. Although the attempted escape fails, Delp is wounded while recapturing Jaime.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> His wounds are so severe that <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Vyman\" title=\"Vyman\">Vyman</a> fears he will die.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Delp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Shortly after Delp's wound has healed and he returns to duty, he is killed during Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Karstark\" title=\"Rickard Karstark\">Rickard Karstark</a>'s murder of <a href=\"/index.php/Willem_Lannister\" title=\"Willem Lannister\">Willem Lannister</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tion_Frey\" title=\"Tion Frey\">Tion Frey</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Delp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_39\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 39\">Chapter 39</a>, Catelyn V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_20\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 20\">Chapter 20</a>, Catelyn III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403122502\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.106 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.374 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 582/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10467/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4779/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 562/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1266/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.250/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.45 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  361.034      1 -total\n 95.80%  345.862      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.13%  343.451      1 Template:Infobox\n 13.39%   48.335     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.02%   14.526      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.24%   11.687      3 Template:Ref\n  2.14%    7.710      3 Template:Ref/core\n  1.55%    5.612      1 Template:Date\n  0.84%    3.025      1 Template:References\n  0.25%    0.898      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:4537-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403122502 and revision id 310905\n -->\n",
